Виктор Львович фон Цур-Мюлен http://russianestonia.eu/index.php?title=%D0%A6%D1%83%D1%80-%D0%9C%D1%8E%D0%BB%D0%B5%D0%BD_%D0%92%D0%B8%D0%BA%D1%82%D0%BE%D1%80_%D0%9B%D1%8C%D0%B2%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B8%D1%87_%D1%84%D0%BE%D0%BD

